{"tid":2151684,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"出口美國港商品改貼中國製標籤　鍾國斌: 影響不大","createTime":"2020-08-11T13:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T02:00:54.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"04143fbed2dd3f76a6d4dc9d327e11dc4fa47819","tid":2151684,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:38:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543108-20200811.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543108-20200811.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FqZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=a335036e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543108-20200811.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5b59c914\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543108-20200811.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國當局要求所有香港製造並出口到美國的商品，由9月底起必須貼上「中國製造」的標籤。自由黨紡織及製衣界議員鍾國斌相信，對本港影響不大，估計會影響本港製造的食品及藥物。<br />\n<br />\n鍾國斌指，本港直接出口美國的貨量不大，例如服裝界大部分的生產線都位處內地，但外地較多人購買本港出產的食品及藥物，例如月餅，新措施會令美國買家不能分辨產地來源。<br />\n<br />\n根據本港《出口（產地來源證）規例》， 工業貿易署可為任何在香港製造、加工或生產而輸出香港的物品，發出產地來源證。鍾國斌表示，政府可能要修例，令出口美國的本港產品，產地來源證符合美國要求，估計短期內難以出口本港貨品到美國。"},{"pid":"968010122406698f8f999085a713baa2f55fbef4","tid":2151684,"uid":220942,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:49:56.000Z","msg":"都冇貨係made in hk<br />\n有算有，都係鄰國運黎香港代工，再痴個mase in hk tag啦"},{"pid":"ee8e1d2f59af3fe7793f5b721c6cd719cc730bd8","tid":2151684,"uid":43939,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:50:56.000Z","msg":"又影響不大 屌你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5f84dbcb7503acb67529bdd925e92f7a915475b","tid":2151684,"uid":333199,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ee8e1d2f59af3fe7793f5b721c6cd719cc730bd8","tid":2151684,"uid":43939,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:50:56.000Z","msg":"又